<li>David P. Chandler: <i>Brother Number One: A political biography of Pol Pot</i>. Westview Press, Boulder, Col. 1992. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0813335108" class="internal">ISBN 0-8133-3510-8</a></li>
