<li>Ben Kiernan: <i>How Pol Pot came to power: A history of Cambodian communism, 1930-1975</i>. New Haven, Conn.: Yale University Press 2004. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0300102623" class="internal">ISBN 0-300-10262-3</a></li>
